                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nA low-fiber diet places less strain on the intestines because this type of diet is easier to digest. Clients need to avoid high-fiber foods when experiencing acute diverticulitis. As the attack resolves, fiber can be added gradually to the diet.",
